  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Males and females subjects of 20-50 years.

          -  Patients with multiple gingival recession (2-4 teeth) of class I &amp; II in maxillary
             teeth.

          -  Patients with well aligned teeth

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with class III &amp;IV gingival recession in maxillary teeth

          -  Recession in relation to molars

          -  Patients with systemic diseases

          -  Medically compromised patients

          -  Patient with history of smoking

          -  Patients with erosion and root caries
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
